  caller_name: Roman
  caller_dialogue: Hi, um, me and my roommate have been hearing his dog outside our
    dorm. Admin told us not to worry about it, but it's getting louder. I think I've
    also heard my sister. Last time I called, the lady told me not to worry, yet
    there's a sound that just keeps getting closer to the dorm. It sounds like someone's
    lugging a dead body, and it's making us go insane. Please help
  correct_answer: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 778c42b10f1dee14c8e0f595f860da28, type: 2}
